{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"08bf11f5b3","title":"关于批判黑《修养》","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a637c773f5","index":0,"year":1967,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"08bf11f5b3"},{"id":"b4db93aa6c","index":1,"year":4,"month":4,"day":null,"articleId":"08bf11f5b3"}],"tags":[{"id":"3aaab89c2a","name":"刘少奇","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961年-1968年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a385a0dc3b","type":"paragraph","text":"关于批判黑《修养》","index":0,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"08bf11f5b3"},{"id":"4262db5f8b","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年三月、四月）","index":1,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"08bf11f5b3"},{"id":"15bbb4d89b","type":"paragraph","text":"（）","index":2,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"08bf11f5b3"},{"id":"70e470ab9e","type":"paragraph","text":"千万不要再上《修养》那本书的当。《修养》这本书，是欺人之谈，脱离现实的阶级斗争，脱离革命，股离政治斗争，闭口不谈革命的根本问题是政权问题，闭口不谈无产阶级专政问题，宣扬唯心主义的修养论，转弯抹角地提倡资产阶级个人主义，提倡奴隶主义，反对马克思列宁主义、毛泽东思想。按照这本书去“修养”，只能是越养越“修”，越修养越成为修正主义。","index":3,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"08bf11f5b3"},{"id":"6eae69d0d2","type":"paragraph","text":"（转摘自《红旗》杂志一九六七年第五期评论员文章）","index":4,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"08bf11f5b3"},{"id":"9fc1f2e33a","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）","index":5,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"08bf11f5b3"},{"id":"4d058d6570","type":"paragraph","text":"这本书完全是欺人之谈。革命的基本问题，就是政权问题。到底要不要夺取政权，能不能夺取政权，怎样夺取政权，对于这些基本问题，这个小册子（即《修养》）避而不谈。根本不谈夺取政权，不谈无产阶级专政，离开了政权，离开了阶级，离开了阶级分析，离开了阶级斗争，完全是一本资产阶级唯心主义的、反动的、不触及蒋介石一根毫毛的东西，是一株资产阶级的大毒草。","index":6,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"08bf11f5b3"},{"id":"a2b97f0e7d","type":"paragraph","text":"（四月十三日康生同志在军委扩大会议上的讲话）","index":7,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"08bf11f5b3"},{"id":"51ff75aa2f","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）","index":8,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"08bf11f5b3"},{"id":"ff953e0779","type":"paragraph","text":"刘少奇的《论共产党员的修养》我看过几逼，这是反马列主义的。我看大学生应该更好的研究一下，选几段写文章批判。要批判刘少奇的《论共产党员的修养》和邓小平多年来的讲酷。","index":9,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"08bf11f5b3"},{"id":"51eca2b4d3","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）","index":10,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"08bf11f5b3"},{"id":"e892b2ce0d","type":"paragraph","text":"四月七日《北京日报》论《打倒反动的“明服工具论”》发表的当天，毛主席说：我从来就不同意“服工具论”。","index":11,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"08bf11f5b3"},{"id":"a8731adbc8","type":"paragraph","text":"（四月九日传达）不能放囊对党内最大走育本主义","index":12,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"08bf11f5b3"},{"id":"4939a32cfe","type":"paragraph","text":"道路当权派的斗争","index":13,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"08bf11f5b3"},{"id":"db5f124a7b","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年四月）我个人党得目前存在这样一个苗头，就是放弃对敌人斗争，对最大的党内走资本主义道·300。","index":14,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"08bf11f5b3"}],"page":{"id":"25069e447e","publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"08bf11f5b3","start":313,"end":313}}}},"__N_SSG":true}